nl.esciencecenter.xenon.engine

Class Adaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.esciencecenter.xenon.engine.Adaptor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FtpAdaptor, LocalAdaptor, ScriptingAdaptor, SshAdaptor, WebdavAdaptor

    public abstract class Adaptor
extends java.lang.Object
    New-style adaptor interface. Adaptors are expected to implement one or more create functions of the Xenon interface, depending on which functionality they provide.
